{"tid":1322781,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"集氣推到樓上找數","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:08:36.000Z","uid":171877,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a50d1bd0278d49ea54feb3888690b0df660b7e1","tid":1322781,"uid":171877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到專家Dickson條友出咗個廣告<br />\n係買&quot;樓上&quot;嘅芒果雪條<br />\n話去到100K 個like就可以有$1雪條食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個大膽既諗法<br />\n號召全部巴絲一人一like<br />\n食窮樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我計過條數，佢地用原片芒果做<br />\n當佢成本$5一個芒果，一人可以買5支，十萬人去買呢到都2球半<br />\n仲未計包裝袋、膠袋果D<br />\n我當佢$2成本，呢啲再多一球<br />\n根本點計佢都係蝕住做<br />\n<br />\n如果到最後真係集氣成功<br />\n睇佢瀨嘢都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地個post都暗示左最後會改易啲食到$1 (奸笑)"},{"pid":"72f74cae99bddad8afbe486f8480376cca405cc8","tid":1322781,"uid":3204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"呢D時間會搵草日老師同100毛做宣傳都算良心企業架啦, 而家落去食支雪條先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chaoyat/posts/2562387970452607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchaoyat%2Fposts%2F2562387970452607&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=15c474e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chaoyat/posts/2562387970452607</a>"},{"pid":"51e62b126c0affe873c999fb655b3a43295c0981","tid":1322781,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"你真係天真<br />\n$2 包裝成本?<br />\n我可以同你講, 成本應該大概係$0.5 以下, 仲要講緊如果返大陸做既話會再平<br />\n至於芒果我就未做過啦, 其他水果既成本都係同你想像中差好遠, 我估一定唔洗$5"},{"pid":"63bc23a52b2deab40088ab5b08a77e39cbf061f0","tid":1322781,"uid":39734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"計埋一支雪條咁大批, 成本$3都唔知洗唔洗<br />\n但可以有100k like<br />\nfacebook廣告都做唔到呢個效益<br />\n<br />\n不過呢, 欣賞佢用100毛, liked"},{"pid":"53bfb19e2221dc580baecfd6560ea30d31b247b4","tid":1322781,"uid":171744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"你呢度仲未計燈油火蠟呢<br />\n同意巴打講法<br />\n班marketing友肯定冇諗過連登集氣上嚟<br />\n威力可以幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b05164d46109027a02d1ee7ee24ec13f6c6619","tid":1322781,"uid":171873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"咪癲啦，你估樓上個老闆智障架咩 條數佢唔識計？蝕本野會照做？"},{"pid":"2df6e8b26e3f9eaab639930e0e1f443beb81629e","tid":1322781,"uid":173216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b05164d46109027a02d1ee7ee24ec13f6c6619","tid":1322781,"uid":171873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"咪癲啦，你估樓上個老闆智障架咩 條數佢唔識計？蝕本野會照做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"老闆蝕住做, 至在大家食得開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387d86ce53eac79790854d7363fafc30e1691423","tid":1322781,"uid":171873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df6e8b26e3f9eaab639930e0e1f443beb81629e","tid":1322781,"uid":173216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b05164d46109027a02d1ee7ee24ec13f6c6619","tid":1322781,"uid":171873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"咪癲啦，你估樓上個老闆智障架咩 條數佢唔識計？蝕本野會照做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"老闆蝕住做, 至在大家食得開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，我又想睇下佢蝕到入肉個樣係點"}]}